        } else {
            halt
        }
    }
}
""".stripMargin)
This event will ensure that a job runs automatically when the "condition1" condition is met. If the condition is not met, the job will not be executed. 

Another way to visualize the workflow is to create a workflow definition in YAML, which can be easily merged with your repository. In this workflow definition, you can define the steps that will be executed based on events in the repository. For example:
